{"tid":641931,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"行快線行得慢嘅撚樣入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-04-25T11:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T16:01:24.000Z","uid":140470,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"17261dd3fdc83d8eb2898f922e7524143b81073e","tid":641931,"uid":140470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:16:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 開110 你班仆街明明前面冇車都開90<br />\n我cut中線爬頭 你班撚樣就高轉大油<br />\n屌你老母 唔撚一早加速 <br />\n<br />\n今日有個冚家剷萬事得<br />\n我都冇推尾cut中線過<br />\n條撚樣就畀油 乘客位條撚屌仲要伸中指<br />\n你咁想玩同你玩 <br />\n個撚樣去中線我開70 <br />\n條撚樣又唔撚爬頭 隔我成3個車位<br />\n玩撚到入機場<br />\n<br />\n仲有Cut線永撚遠唔撚打燈班的士狗<br />\n成日唔撚打燈 話插就插 當我雞"},{"pid":"2cedc99524f811207f189ce22fcfb3c491f1d265","tid":641931,"uid":8867,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6892e1d2e168deb9aaa1b846dc6b1457771bede9","tid":641931,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"所以係香港揸車一定係大cc<br />\nV8 biturbo岩岩好"},{"pid":"2b211aa66b7493a3b4bd7ce3c0a24aed9d432868","tid":641931,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"cut線唔打燈可摸耳拎車cam片1823<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bff9a054ad512cdfa048fdb0e3b2d805721ae1","tid":641931,"uid":140470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2cedc99524f811207f189ce22fcfb3c491f1d265","tid":641931,"uid":8867,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:23:19.000Z","msg":"都有嬲 <br />\n不過好想講 揸得慢係可以 唔好太慢<br />\n咁有中線慢線 點解唔去返中慢線行<br />\n見過好多次 唔打燈同快線行得慢"},{"pid":"cc80ccd753326f11a2582e421e00a63f3a8facbe","tid":641931,"uid":140470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2b211aa66b7493a3b4bd7ce3c0a24aed9d432868","tid":641931,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"cut線唔打燈可摸耳拎車cam片1823<img src=\"